SHRK_1A ~z~~r~Debt Collector~w~: Hey, Mr. Johnson, just a friendly reminder that you owe me money!
SHRK_1B ~z~~r~Debt Collector~w~: Don't be a stranger!

SHRK_2A ~z~~r~Debt Collector~w~: Hello, Carl Johnson!
SHRK_2B ~z~~r~Debt Collector~w~: You owe me money and I would consider it polite if you paid it back, understand?

SHRK_3A ~z~~r~Debt Collector~w~: Mr. Carl Johnson, my records show that you owe me money!
SHRK_3B ~z~~r~Debt Collector~w~: Probably just slipped your mind, but I thought I'd just jog your memory!

SHRK_4A ~z~~r~Debt Collector~w~: Mr. Johnson, I haven't seen you for a while and you owe me money!
SHRK_4B ~z~~r~Debt Collector~w~: Consider your position and that of your friends and family!

SHRK_5A ~z~~r~Debt Collector~w~: Carl, I hope you're not spending too much cash! Especially since you've owed me money for so long!
SHRK_5B ~z~~r~Debt Collector~w~: Don't make an enemy of me, Carl!

SHRK_6A ~z~~r~Debt Collector~w~: Carl Johnson, I hear you have a sister!
SHRK_6B ~z~~r~Debt Collector~w~: Don't make me explain to her why you owe me so much money!

SHRK_7A ~z~~r~Debt Collector~w~: I'm a patient man, Mr. Johnson, but I'm also a businessman, understand?
SHRK_7B ~z~~r~Debt Collector~w~: You owe me money, Carl! Think about it!

SHRK_8A ~z~~r~Debt Collector~w~: Mr. Johnson, you owe me money!
SHRK_8B ~z~~r~Debt Collector~w~: A business relationship is built on trust and mutual respect! Think about it!

SHRK_9A ~z~~r~Debt Collector~w~: Mr. Johnson, I hear you're in the neighborhood!
SHRK_9B ~z~~r~Debt Collector~w~: Some of my associates will be paying you a visit to talk about your debts!

SHRK10A ~z~~r~Debt Collector~w~: Carl Johnson, little bird told me you're in town!
SHRK10B ~z~~r~Debt Collector~w~: You should have listened to me and paid your debts!

SHRK11A ~z~~r~Debt Collector~w~: A man of honor pays his debts, Mr. Johnson!
SHRK11B ~z~~r~Debt Collector~w~: You've left me no choice but to treat you with the same lack of respect you've shown me!

SHRK12A ~z~~r~Debt Collector~w~: I am not a charity, Mr. Johnson, I'm a businessman!
SHRK12B ~z~~r~Debt Collector~w~: You should have paid up while you had the chance!

SHRK13A ~z~~r~Debt Collector~w~: Mr. Johnson, I want my fucking money!
SHRK13B ~z~~r~Debt Collector~w~: I'm sending someone round to pay you a little courtesy call!

SHRK14A ~z~~r~Debt Collector~w~: I don't think you're getting the message, Mr. Johnson... I WANT MY MONEY!
SHRK14B ~z~~r~Debt Collector~w~: I'll let you negotiate with my, eh... collection department!

SHRK15A ~z~~r~Debt Collector~w~: The time for pleasantries is past, Mr. Johnson!
SHRK15B ~z~~r~Debt Collector~w~: You've given me no choice but to get a little more persuasive about your debt problems!

SHRK16A ~z~~r~Debt Collector~w~: You had your chance to pay me, Mr. Johnson!
SHRK16B ~z~~r~Debt Collector~w~: You've left me no option in this matter... I WANT MY MONEY!

